  "text": "Extreme Learning Machine (ELM) [CITATION_1] : The ELM network is a recent development in the field of neural computation. Its main idea is to combine the nonlinear pattern recognition power of multilayer feedforward networks with a fast training algorithm. In terms of topology and parameters, ELM is exactly equal to the one-hidden-layered MLP network, with linear output neurons.",
